economic.translate: экономический, хозяйственный, экономичный, экономный, экономически выгодный
examples: History is the product of social and economic forces.
There seems to be no cure for our economic ills.
The war has aggravated an acute economic crisis.
Economic plight is far worse than had been expected.
Cutting taxes may facilitate economic recovery.
The recent economic crisis has led to massive layoffs.
People attach too much importance to economic forecasts.
The country is in economic stasis.
an economic use of home heating oil
The country is an economic backwater.
an economical use of her time
the economic vitality of our cities
He implemented a new economic plan.
a critique of modern economic theory
